primarys.simple_primary: " This example tests the configuration of two flow machines that are installed in parallel. Both flow machines start with full speed. At t=150 second, the speed of the flow machine on the top is reduced to zero. As its speed is reduced, the mass flow rate changes its direction in such a way that the flow machine at the top has reverse flow. "

"
